This is your Play application
=============================

To run tests
-------------

sbt clean test

To run
-------

sbt run

Endpoints
=========

GET /getAllClients
--------------------

returns all clients from the database

GET /getAllPets
-----------------

returns all clients from the database

GET /getAllItems
-----------------

returns all items (for now, just a copy of getAllClients) from the database


POST /registerNewPet
----------------------

example payload:
{
    "firstName": "fName",
    "lastName": "lName",
    "petName": "Floofy",
    "petNotes": "Happy, Hairy and Healthy"
}

adds a client and a pet to the database

